1 Tuner + 1 or more non-Tuner monsters Once per turn: You can banish 1 Plant-Type monster from your Graveyard, then target 1 face-up monster your opponent controls; halve that target's ATK, until the end of this turn. During the Battle Phase, if this card attacked: You can banish 1 Plant-Type monster in your Graveyard; halve this card's ATK until the end of this turn, and if you do, this card can make a second attack during this Battle Phase.
